data.description: BACK ON THE MARKET! Buyer got cold feet before inspections, so there's another chance at this adorable 3 bedroom, 2 bath home conveniently located near I-240 giving easy access to Tinker AFB, the airport, downtown OKC, tons of restaurants and shopping areas and really anywhere in the metro area.  The home features a huge living room with a beautiful fireplace, and a large separate dining area.  The kitchen recently got a brand-new backsplash to update the space.  There is an indoor utility room with storage and a large two car garage with extra space and a work bench!  Just off the living and dining room there is an added bonus of an enclosed patio that is not included in the square footage.  All three bedrooms have access to a bathroom.  Two of the bedrooms also have brand new flooring.  Several rooms have been painted within the last year as well.  The HVAC was also replaced in 2022!  The fridge & mounted TV are negotiable.  THE SELLER NEEDS TO GET THIS SOLD SO BRING AN OFFER TO US!!
